@startuml
[*] --> Order
state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance

Order --> Arrival : plane arrived
Arrival --> Preparation : plane transitioned
Preparation --> Operations : plane assigned
Operations --> Maintenance : no scheduled flights
Maintenance --> Preparation : plane serviced
Preparation --> Operations : plane ready for operations
Operations --> Maintenance : maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : plane serviced
Order --> [*] : plane removed

@enduml
